keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map ge scrollToBottom
map <c-h> goBack
map <c-l> goForward
map h goBack
map l goForward
map e Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map E Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab
